[The YF outbreak in Sudan has spread from Southern Kordofan State to the
neighboring states since the beginning of November 2005. Southern Kordofan
state is located in the center of Sudan. (see map:
<http://www.un.org/Depts/Cartographic/map/profile/sudan.pdf>)
- Mod.RY]
